{
  "stem": "10.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he saved me my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because SS men, they would kill me, see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he saved me my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't intervene anymore, because they see he's working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for weeks and weeks, I couldn't lay down on my back, only on the stomach and leg-- [LAUGHS] till it was healing up, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he saved my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this went on-- yeah, this is what got worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We Jews, when we returned from work, it was evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We marched back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after the roll call, all other prisoners could go to the back, to the blocks, to barracks-- relax, get their food, and go to bed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We Jews had to remain outside and work in the camp, enlarge the camp till 12 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came to the barrack, we didn't care anymore about the food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just fell on our straw sacks, and we fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we didn't eat, see?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first two months-- the first six months, we never had a drop of water to wash ourselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave you soap from the beginning, but there was never water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the morning, when we got this little container with the coffee, we left a few drops just to wet our eyes and finger-- the nails-- the-- the tips-- the fingertips.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Naturally, we never changed our underwear in six months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in no time, typhus epidemic broke out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were getting weaker and weaker And about two years later, in October '40-- no, one year here later-- in October '42, we formed a transport of 17 people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So from those 400 who came a year before to Gross-Rosen, 17 were we-- we were alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's all that remained.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
